			Company Description 


			trivago NV is a holding company, which engages in the provision of a global hotel search platform. The firm offers a website and a mobile application under the trivago brand. It also provides marketing tools and services for advertisers such as trivago Hotel Manager and trivago Intelligence. The com...
		


                trivago NV is a holding company, which engages in the provision of a global hotel search platform. The firm offers a website and a mobile application under the trivago brand. It also provides marketing tools and services for advertisers such as trivago Hotel Manager and trivago Intelligence. The company is headquartered in Düsseldorf, Germany.
            




