Company Summary
trivago N.V. is a technology company. It provides internet-related services and products in the fields of hotels, lodging and metasearch. trivago N.V. is based in Duesseldorf, Germany.   





 





Trivago NV: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















trivago nv
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Internet Based Services
Trivago N.V. provides online hotel search platform. The Company, through its platform, offers price information, reviews, photos, booking, and other travel services. Trivago serves customers worldwide.




